--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 512a72de08c75cf4e8a8424f7b75a271, type: 3}
  m_Name: D1T3_AdvisorFirstTalk
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  npc: 0
  sequence:
  - dialogueText: You're holding up. Most guys look like they've seen a ghost after
      ten minutes with this job
    buttonText: I'm fine
  - dialogueText: Good. It's better to be a ghost yourself in a place like this.
      You see things, but nobody sees you
    buttonText: I see plenty
  - dialogueText: I bet. But the Boss... he only lets you see what he wants. He's
      got you cleaning glass while the island moves right under your nose
    buttonText: The island?
  - dialogueText: There are things out there. Pills... Tucked away where the tourists
      don't go. If you can handle them for me, you're more than just a waiter
    buttonText: Handle them?
  - dialogueText: A trust exercise. Keep your mouth shut and your eyes wide open.
      We'll talk about the details when...
    buttonText: When?
  - dialogueText: Wait... Don't look now, but the Boss is waving at you. He's got
      that "next job" look.
    buttonText: He wants me?
  - dialogueText: Yeah. Move. Whatever he says, just nod. We'll finish this conversation
      when the smoke clears
    buttonText: I'm moving
